Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.40,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.98,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.24,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.12,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.79,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.17,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.18,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:04.77,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.49,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:27.00,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)\move(360,440,137.25,440,2200,4500)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even more convinced now, I love you.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.57,0:02:11.58,Default,EP title,0,0,150,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HE3C4A2&\t(0,1100,\bord0.11\blur0.4\3c&H945431&)\c&HF7EEF0&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx167\fscy157}Episode 2 \N\N\NMy 19th Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1200,0)}The sea, you say? \NThat'd be great...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I have to attend the club every day. \NMy "menu" is very strict...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? And that's gonna stop you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Katsura is at the shrine again, right? \NNo one else can stop you from going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Practices can wait for a while, but house by the sea can't!\N There will be eight guys and three other girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see we have a shortage without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine how eager everyone is \Nabout meeting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, but I really can't be absent for three days. \NI might get a call while I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you getting a call from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,800)}You just said, "I might get a call while I'm there." \NWhom from? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,20,,{\fade(700,0)\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Amateur champion Takayuki leaves the country
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to deny now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm intrigued...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who is he? \NI don't believe you meant coach Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,900)}Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me... what is happening to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone, and why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,TV only gave me the idea of your plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention to become a pro... \NYour intention to drop out of university...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried so hard, but I couldn't reach you by phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you now have \Nmore important matters on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But just a single call... would have been enough \Nto relieve my soul from something that oppresses it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause since that rainy morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't say a word to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ms. Oka Hiromi, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if that seems inconvenient to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a "Sports Toto" journalist, and I hope you won't mind \Na quick interview if we give you a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo will be the subject. \NMs. Oka, you both graduated from Nishi High, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are writing a short biography of your friend Todo. \NWe have already talked to a few of his close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but when I came to him today \Nfor a personal interview, he politely refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Came to him?{\i0} Todo didn't tell anyone his whereabouts. \NHave you found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna lie, he's good at hiding, \Nbut we are even better at seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you please share \Nthe location of Todo with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! But take it easy, \Nwe're the ones supposed to interview people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Todo, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,moved to Kamakura, \Nto one of the Buddhist shrines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, though I never heard he was religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi? Are you leaving again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm... \NI'm going to coach Katsura's shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,His training instructions are unclear to me, \Nso I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You will pay him a visit that late? \NWon't you at least have dinner with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But have you warned him? \NYou sure you won't disturb him that late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also starting to rain. \NHow about you come back now and go there tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The racket should be shrieking while cutting the air. \NWith great power comes control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you keep complaining, \Ndon't even dare to dream about improving your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If your training is indulgent, \Nyou are no national championship winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, my dear, if it will destroy your hopes, but all men \Nare the same, and only a few among them are unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the main thing \Nis not to give up and keep looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! We all wish Ms. Wei from Yamashita good luck! \NAnd now a letter from Shimano, from Ms. Keiko! Let's read.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm convinced the love is dead..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Already interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"My sister is a traitor, and I was so blind! \NI don't want to see my sister! I only want to die..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, in two weeks he is leaving for America \Nto continue his training there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In just two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, \Nhe wanted something else done. Here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to fear, Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the training plan I left you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here? You should be at "Park Hill" now, \Nperforming power training upon my instructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly why I'm here! I can't take it anymore! \NThis lonesome practice drives me crazy, therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, I beg you to let me continue training here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I'll be engaged every day \Nand won't cause any inconvenience!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka... Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't banish you out of here, \Nbut you're gonna have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... be prepared that I'll have no spare time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume you took your two weeks' belongings with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay in the room \Nwhere you used to live before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a talent! Chiba, I had no idea \Nyou are that skilled in playing the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in middle school \Nwhen parents first made me take lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The piano was your first passion, \Nbut then you switched to the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo and I... \NHave met not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I let him know about your demand for a meet. \NHe expressed no objections, you can visit him anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But be aware that he is now preoccupied \Nwith pro-test preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With coach Katsura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... One of our mutual acquaintances \Ninformed me where to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are going to meet Todo... \NDo you mind if Ozaki and I will accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, if you wish to. \NBut what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To avert injustice towards him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Injustice? I was just going to have a talk with Todo. \NI doubt this meet will have anything in need of averting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly, you have objections \Nagainst him becoming a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You have received a lot of sponsorship offers, \Nbut you aren't trying to become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a matter of my personal judgment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me then, \Nwhat will you say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you be questioning his decisions, \Nhis personal judgment? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some very wrong ideas about me, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Ozaki are not the only ones \Nto call him a time-proven friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,During our education at Nishi High, \Nwe played countless matches in doubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that making just two thousand swings \Nmight be enough to call it a day and ease up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You still lack confidence in your hands, \Nand your timings are in need of a lot of polish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The power should guide your racket \Nsince you're an overripe player already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An overripe player?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo is already overripe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that Todo in his early twenties \Nis an overripe already... How is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1250)}Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}I'm glad to see you're doing fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Since our last meeting, \NI have called your phone countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,TV made me worry about you... \Nwhen they said you're becoming a pro and going abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But... since our last rainy encounter back then, \Nfor some reason you seemed so hurt and lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How happy I was... \Nto find out I wasn't the reason for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your becoming a pro isn't the consequence for my rude words, \Nbut your own well-thought decision. And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly worried about it all. I have no idea what to do. \NOf course, I still love you no matter what... But for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If things go that way, \Nand we'll have to part again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine what should I think, what should I do... \NEven the idea of breaking the bond with you brings pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine no matter what, Todo. There's just some inexplicable anxiety about your journey, in my chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Coach, I brought this with me. \NPlease treat yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, you too. \NHave some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called "Sports Drink." With orange, pine, peach...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with one thousand serves and strength exercises!? \NWhy aren't you on the roadwork now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already finished it! \NI got up early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rest now. \NGo to your room and save energy for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sports drink, want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, my dear Maki... \NI hope you're spending your days as great as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget this nineteenth summer of my life, have my word!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause the summer spent \Nin such a beautiful place one certainly can’t forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I have a wholesome climate, wholesome food, \Nand wholesome company! What else is needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, even that is not the main reason, \Nwhy I'll remember this nineteenth summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something even more special happened here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, in ten years or so, \NI could tell you the whole story...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for now. \NWholeheartedly yours, H.O."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you begin avoiding our company, Todo? \NAnd what's the reason behind your silent demeanor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have created so many bright memories together... \NIn the courts of our high school and the tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us know the truth, Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How come that after finishing the climb, one doesn't stop \Nto catch their breath? Why do they continue to climb ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that "the climb is finished"? \NWho said such nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If Todo... becomes a real player, \Nit will not be the end, but rather the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea at all \Nfor what is waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause in the pro world, no matter how hard you try, \Nyou only reap suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you deliberately doom yourself to this. \NWhat for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Madame Butterfly! \N- Chiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't keep us in ignorance, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What delusion forces you to climb further without us? \NI'm begging you to explain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Katsura, you should understand \Nwhat I'm talking about better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you trying to convey to Todo \Nthe idea of how wrong he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We both understand that Todo is an overripe already. \NWhy aren't you stopping him from going to the pro world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to stop him. \NTodo chose this path himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly, I don't get it at all! \NTodo is just twenty-one years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like me, Todo started playing tennis \Nat the age of eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From the age of eight, \Nwe both started spending all day long on the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make the idea clearer for you now? \NIn middle school, we regularly won prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For six high school years, one should rise \Nall the way up to his regions' top of the players.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make the idea clearer for you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The speed of reflexes, the strength of the serve, \Nthe strength of the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In boxing, athletes are retiring when they are this old, \Nand tennis is no less severe sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wake up and see that you are \Nabout ten years late to the world's top!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if you start climbing at twenty-odd years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The time when thirty-year players \Ncould make it there is long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tennis is so extreme that its future champions \Nare being trained from infancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So they come to their peak prepared. \NBut you are already past it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, but what if Todo could just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo... You and I really had a chance to become pros \Nif we started to strive for it back in middle school, but not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When the peak of our strength was about to come! \NNot at present when everything is behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, in the pro world, our experience and technique \Nwouldn't stand a single compare to a common player's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our best efforts will have no effect at all! \NDon't you still get it, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to do it despite everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you still choose this foredoomed path?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For the same reason... \Ncoach Munakata then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,started to teach tennis the newbie Oka \Nand not the experienced me, which drove me mad at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the first-year then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:18:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But only recently I realized I was already on my peak \Nat that time, and had nowhere to rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That used to frenzy me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was certain that I will never forgive coach Munakata, \Neven if he would try to make amends for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo... I love tennis no less than you do. Tennis is \Nmy whole life, but I don’t dare to dream about becoming a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As an amateur, you can always play tennis at your own pace, \Neven for your whole life, if you wish to. Just like I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am worried about your future, \Nwith all my heart. Like a true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Madame Butterfly. Thank you... There's not a single thesis \Nin your statement that I could argue with. Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems there's no point \Nconcealing even personal issues from old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have \Ntalked to you earlier. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When Munakata Jin fell ill and quit sports, \Nhe was about twenty-one years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That is... pretty much my age now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,had Mr. Munakata eluded his incurable disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he would continue his professional career? \NWhat is your opinion? That is my only question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have become world-famous, \Nworking and sweating without a hint of fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But fate had other plans... He fell sick and then left us... \NOne genius player Munakata Jin, who raised us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So as his student, I feel the need \Nto continue what he began but couldn't finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I have to do this \Nas the one wielding a still healthy body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was initially prepared to face the fact \NI might be too weak to reach the end either...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At the age of twenty-one, he was forced to back off \Nfrom this path, but I will continue it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything Madame Butterfly said is right. \NThe peak of my strength is already in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Munakata played his first tennis match when \Nhe entered high school. But I play since I was only eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be very well the truth \Nthat in terms of tennis I'm already an elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However... \NHowever, I thought it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in the choice that Mr. Munakata did \Nbecause he saw the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And this faith he put into my heart too, \Nso I cannot give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try again. If I have reached my peak already, \NI can definitely get there once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My decision to quit university... \NThe decision to become a pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't lie, I hesitated a lot. \NBut in the end, I chose to go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When if not today? \NOne should not put off until later what he can do now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For I don’t want Munakata Jin to become just an intangible \Nmemory for us! He shouldn't be forgotten like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,While what he started is still alive... \NI believe... While we keep moving, he is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Oka? \NI thought you were staying for two weeks straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. \NI'd better go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That place is so crowded because of me, \Nit might interrupt your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But tell me, Todo will clearly pass his pro-test, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who knows... 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is ahead, \Nplease don't give up.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:21.22,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:26.85,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.81,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:32.69,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:37.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.79,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:50.17,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:57.05,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:03.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:12.66,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.86,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:20.91,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.95,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:29.48,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Make here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The day when Todo embarkes on his long journey is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should not be sad about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We should keep our chins up!\NRight, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine, on the day of departure, coach Katsura organizes \Na training match with Madame Butterfly. What a heartless coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.25,0:23:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You might run out of time to say goodbye to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "Never Say Goodbye."
